name: Successfully purchase items using Efecty

children.description: Given the user is on the mac-center.com platform using "chrome"
Johan open main
Johan opens the browser at https://mac-center.com/

When adds the following items to the cart
| Iphone 15 pro max |
| Apple Watch |
| iPad pro |
Johan search item
Johan clicks on the search box
Johan enters 'Iphone 15 pro max',ENTER into the search box
Johan add item to cart
Johan clicks on [[ChromeDriver: chrome on windows (fdfbcb56713be1222b95514a06725a26)] -> xpath: //button[@data-available = 'Agregar al carrito']]
Johan clicks on the close button
Johan search item
Johan clicks on the search box
Johan enters 'Apple Watch',ENTER into the search box
Johan add item to cart
Johan clicks on [[ChromeDriver: chrome on windows (fdfbcb56713be1222b95514a06725a26)] -> xpath: //button[@data-available = 'Agregar al carrito']]
Johan clicks on the close button
Johan search item
Johan clicks on the search box
Johan enters 'iPad pro',ENTER into the search box
Johan add item to cart
Johan clicks on [[ChromeDriver: chrome on windows (fdfbcb56713be1222b95514a06725a26)] -> xpath: //button[@data-available = 'Agregar al carrito']]
Johan clicks on the close button
And goes to the cart
Johan open cart
Johan clicks on the cart link button
Johan clicks on the go to the cart button
Johan confirm cart
Johan clicks on the confirm purchase button
And confirms their credentials using efecty payment method
Johan fill out form
Johan enters 'connie.monahan@yahoo.com' into the email field
Johan selects #value in the id box
Johan enters '10316815321' into the id field
Johan enters 'Elia' into the name field
Johan enters 'Kuphal' into the lastname field
Johan enters 'Suite 467 331 Claud Mill, Thompsonview, FL 15991' into the address field
Johan selects #value in the department box
Johan selects #value in the city box
Johan enters '3164445953' into the phone field
Johan continue to payment
Johan clicks on the continue button
Johan clicks on continue payment button
Johan select efecty option
Johan clicks on continue efecty payment option
Johan fill out efecty form
Johan selects #value in the efecty payment box
Johan selects #value in the efecty document box
Johan enters '10316815321' into the document input
Johan clicks on the terms and conditions check box
Then should be able to confirm the payment
Then pay button enabled should be (true)
